<div class="content" name="IOCSPAdminD" uuid="c34fc93b-c329-48c5-81dc-1a4f0c80bf5c"><p>The IOCSPAdminD interface provides an RPC interface for a
client to manage an <span><a href="801063f5-7eda-4bfe-99ef-84c1ea3849a1#gt_688a239d-e58b-42df-b622-da727dca4227" data-linktype="relative-path">Online Responder</a></span>.</p><p>IOCSPAdminD interface inherits the IUnknown interface.</p><p>The version number for IUnknown is 1.0. The UUID for the
IOCSPAdminD interface is: &#34;784b693d-95f3-420b-8126-365c098659f2&#34;.
Method opnum field values start with 3; opnum values 0 through 2 represent the <span><a href="../ms-dcom/2b4db106-fb79-4a67-b45f-63654f19c54c" data-linktype="relative-path">IUnknown</a></span>
methods: QueryInterface, AddRef, and Release methods inherited from <span><a href="../ms-dcom/4a893f3d-bd29-48cd-9f43-d9777a4415b0" data-linktype="relative-path">[MS-DCOM]</a></span>.
